text: Mick Donohue (2 August 1917 – 15 September 1990) was an Australian rules footballer who played with Collingwood in the Victorian Football League (VFL). == Notes == == External links == * *Profile on Collingwood Forever Category:1917 births Category:1990 deaths Category:Australian rules footballers from Victoria (Australia) Category:Collingwood Football Club players
